    "description": "State file for DMSi Capability Map (capability-map.html). Edit this file to change capability confidence labels and stage status/blockers without editing the HTML.",
    "usage": {
      "capabilities": "Each capability has an id (wm, vi, pd, pa, ls, wsb, wsc, wsd) and a confidence label. Allowed values: discovery (gray), on-track (green), at-risk (amber), behind (red).",
