    "notes": "If a stage is omitted from the stages array, the map uses the default status/blockers from the HTML. To control every stage, include an entry for each capabilityId + num. Future: this structure can be generated from Jira (epic status -> confidence; issue status -> stage status; blocking issues -> blockers)."
